OL,4,Cfaced parcel delivery problem in last
OL,5,Cmonth'
OL,7,FMore than a third of online shoppers `
OL,8,Falmost 15 million people ` experienced
OL,9,Fa problem with a parcel delivery in
OL,10,Fthe last month, according to an annual
OL,11,FCitizens Advice study.
OL,13,FJust before a Black Friday and
OL,14,FChristmas shopping surge, the charity
OL,15,Fsaid its survey revealed a "worrying
OL,16,Ftrend" of worsening customer service
OL,17,Famong delivery firms.
