OL,5,Cmonth'
OL,7,FThe Citizens Advice parcels league
OL,8,Ftable looks at the top five delivery
OL,9,Fcompanies by parcel volume and
OL,10,Fmeasures their performance against
OL,11,Fcustomer service, delivery problems
OL,12,Fand how well they meet the needs of
OL,13,Fconsumers who have extra accessibility
OL,14,Fneeds, such as needing longer to
OL,15,Fanswer the door.
OL,17,FIts survey suggests 36% of all online
OL,18,Fshoppers in the UK experienced a
OL,19,Fdelivery issue in the last month, such
OL,20,Fas parcels left in insecure locations
OL,21,Fand arriving late.
