OL,4,Cfaced parcel delivery problem in last
OL,5,Cmonth'
OL,7,FThe worst offenders were Yodel (42%),
OL,8,FDPD (40%) and Evri (37%), according to
OL,9,Fthe poll.
OL,11,FOf those who experienced a problem
OL,12,Fwith their delivery, 48% had a further
OL,13,Fissue trying to resolve it ` the
OL,14,Fhighest level for three years `
OL,15,Fincluding not being able to find the
OL,16,Fright company contact details or not
OL,17,Freceiving a response.
OL,19,FAll providers except DPD saw their
OL,20,Fscore on customer service decline in
OL,21,Fthe last year.
